Gotham City Sirens is an American comic book series was written by Paul Dini with art by Guillem March and published by DC Comics .
The term Gotham City Sirens refers to three of the most popular female characters that inhabit Gotham City , which include Catwoman , Harley Quinn , and Poison Ivy .
The first issue of the series was released in June , 2009 , as a part of the Batman : Reborn relaunch in all of DC 's Batman titles .
Warner Bros. is developing a film with the same title , although it has not been announced if the film will be based on the comic book series .